{"tid":1565604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真請各位學識自衛術 特別係前線勇武","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T02:18:36.000Z","uid":58841,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e78f990a970d74f486334c3dd86b3fa05882962a","tid":1565604,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KPIet__oy_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKPIet__oy_A&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=30eb5700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KPIet__oy_A</a><br />\n例如呢條就係教你點反擊持棍警犬<br />\nIKMF係以色列係每個人都必學技黎<br />\n而家香港咁既時勢好應該要學<br />\n特別而家仲有休班狗拎棍周街行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2uc44atkviU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2uc44atkviU&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=19df3280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2uc44atkviU</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學下防身啦仆街</span></span>"},{"pid":"9c595a132c84fb4e561110102f266392d479024e","tid":1565604,"uid":4050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請不要再討論唱歌跳閘，實事派請全面進場。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e26fc41f5848e65a04d336073b0df9b5204490d2","tid":1565604,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:22:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=2cf73bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"9ea84a913cdffd27128c36a22c5e00b96e407df9","tid":1565604,"uid":30374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97a55518d80ee020ad25615c39b2290b9896df44","tid":1565604,"uid":172893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 831"},{"pid":"9b1a9083b613c0d6077b458078af5d6c75e4ffdd","tid":1565604,"uid":46848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d868c9b9390bd12d0c8635c23d6ae0b944211335","tid":1565604,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"好似話對面渣刀都一樣work<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d1993753f705f1b5545c56801bbc5ae758783b","tid":1565604,"uid":281101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"學多樣野冇壞"},{"pid":"81614d61befd435821546e560670ed6049089ed3","tid":1565604,"uid":276839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔洗再講呢啲，佢地都冇膽。"},{"pid":"fc33e4b78326f13d02dc71c690bf97cf9c994ffc","tid":1565604,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,